law.text:
No material shall be incorporated by reference unless:
The material incorporated by reference relates only to the specific subject matter governed by an administrative regulation;
The material has been reviewed in detail by the administrative body;
No statute, state or federal regulation prescribes the same or similar procedure, or sets forth a comprehensive scheme of regulation of the subject matter; and
Its incorporation is necessary in order to:
Implement, interpret, or prescribe law or policy authorized or required by statute;
Establish or describe the organization, procedure, or practice requirements authorized or required by statute.
